a-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-73eb6eb\" data-id=\"73eb6eb\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac855f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac855f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a proud Austin-Area resident for over 30 years, I\u2019ve had a front-row seat to the city\u2019s incredible transformation, from a laid-back college town to one of the nation\u2019s fastest-growing and most dynamic metro areas. Through the highs and lows, from the Dot-com crash of 2000 to the housing downturn of 2008 and the challenges of the 2020 pandemic, one thing has remained true: Austin\u2019s real estate market is resilient, and so are the people who call it home.<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Real estate is more than just a transaction, it\u2019s personal. Whether you\u2019re buying or selling, I know this journey can be deeply emotional and financially significant. That\u2019s why I\u2019m committed to being both your fiercest negotiator and your biggest cheerleader. My goal is to make the process not just successful, but meaningful and as stress-free as possible.<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">My clients often say I go beyond the role of a realtor, they know me as someone who\u2019s loyal, honest, relational, and always in their corner. Many have become lifelong friends, and that\u2019s the heart of what I do: building lasting relationships rooted in trust.<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To better serve my clients, I continue to stay educated and informed, earning several professional designations which include:<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0&#8211; <strong>Graduate, REALTOR\u00ae Institute (GRI)<\/strong><\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; <strong>Accredited Buyer Representative (ABR)<\/strong><\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>&#8211; Certified Full-Service Professional (CFSP)<\/strong><\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These credentials reflect my commitment to providing expert guidance, next-level service, and a smooth, successful experience for every client.<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Originally from Michigan, raised in Colorado, and forever planted in Texas, I landed at TCU on a golf scholarship. Today, I\u2019m a wife, mom to three amazing daughters, avid tennis player, and love pickleball. I\u2019m also the proud schnauzer mom to Boomer, our spirited sidekick. My husband and I own a lumberyard chain, specializing in outdoor living spaces, which keeps us plugged into building trends and adds another layer of insight and value for my clients.<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you\u2019re buying your first home, moving up, or downsizing for a new chapter, I would be honored to guide you through the journey. Your goals matter to me, and so does your experience.<\/p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let\u2019s get started, your next chapter is waiting.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac11626 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"ac11626\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\